ParameterName: The name of the sound instance parameter that specifies the current value.
Default: The default value to be used if the parameter is not found.
MinInput: The minimum input value. Values will be clamped to the [MinInput, MaxInput] range.
MaxInput: The maximum input value. Values will be clamped to the [MinInput, MaxInput] range.
MinOutput: The minimum output value. The input value will be scaled from the range [MinInput, MaxInput] to [MinOut, MaxOutput]
MaxOutput: The maximum output value. The input value will be scaled from the range [MinInput, MaxInput] to [MinOut, MaxOutput]
ParamMode: The mode with which to treat the input value
